// Go workspace for the THIN kite-mcp-server deploy repo.
//
// Post-bootstrap-relocation (2026-05-16), only the root module remains
// in this repo. The 3 prior workspace members (app/providers, plugins,
// testutil) moved to github.com/algo2go/kite-mcp-bootstrap as part of
// the 49,400-LOC mass-move. See:
//   - main.go : 35-line entry point delegating to bootstrap.Main
//   - go.mod  : require + cross-repo replace pointing at
//               ../algo2go/kite-mcp-bootstrap until tagged + published.
//
// Cross-repo workspace inclusion of bootstrap is OPTIONAL during local
// development — uncomment the `use ../algo2go/kite-mcp-bootstrap` line
// below to let `go build ./...` from this repo also re-build bootstrap
// in-tree. The go.mod replace directive alone is enough for the deploy
// repo; the workspace `use` line is purely for cross-repo IDE integration.

go 1.25.0

use .

// To enable cross-repo workspace mode for local IDE + cross-source jumps:
// use ../algo2go/kite-mcp-bootstrap
// use ../algo2go/kite-mcp-bootstrap/app/providers
// use ../algo2go/kite-mcp-bootstrap/plugins
// use ../algo2go/kite-mcp-bootstrap/testutil
